            <div class="testimonial-content">
              <p>"Anjaneya Innovations' expertise in AI and cloud architecture was instrumental in modernizing our platform, significantly improving performance and scalability."</p>
            </div>
            <div class="testimonial-author">
              <p class="name">Alex Chen</p>
              <p class="position">CTO, TechForward Solutions</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Draft Testimonials -->
          <div class="testimonial" data-index="1">
            <div class="testimonial-content">
              <p>"Their strategic insights and agile approach helped us navigate a complex digital transformation smoothly and under budget. True partners."</p>
            </div>
            <div class="testimonial-author">
              <p class="name">Samantha Bee</p>
              <p class="position">CEO, Growth Dynamics</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="testimonial" data-index="2">
            <div class="testimonial-content">
              <p>"The custom software delivered exceeded our expectations, streamlining critical workflows and boosting our team's productivity immensely."</p>
            </div>
            <div class="testimonial-author">
              <p class="name">Raj Patel</p>
              <p class="position">VP Operations, Global Logistics Inc.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="testimonial" data-index="3">
            <div class="testimonial-content">
              <p>"From UX consulting to final UI design, Anjaneya's team demonstrated exceptional skill and a deep understanding of user needs."</p>
            </div>
            <div class="testimonial-author">
              <p class="name">Maria Garcia</p>
              <p class="position">Head of Product, InnovateApp</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="testimonial" data-index="4">
            <div class="testimonial-content">
              <p>"Their fractional CTO service provided invaluable leadership during a critical growth phase. Highly recommended for tech strategy."</p>
            </div>
            <div class="testimonial-author">
              <p class="name">David Lee</p>
              <p class="position">Founder, ScaleUp Ventures</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="testimonial" data-index="5">
            <div class="testimonial-content">
              <p>"Anjaneya helped us optimize our Salesforce implementation, unlocking data insights we didn't know we had. Measurable ROI."</p>
            </div>
            <div class="testimonial-author">
              <p class="name">Fatima Khan</p>
              <p class="position">Director of Sales Ops, ConnectSphere</p>
            </div>
          </div>
           <div class="testimonial" data-index="6">
            <div class="testimonial-content">
              <p>"The AI-driven analytics platform they built gives us a significant competitive edge. Their technical depth is impressive."</p>
            </div>
            <div class="testimonial-author">
              <p class="name">Kenji Tanaka</p>
              <p class="position">Chief Data Officer, Insightful Corp.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
